1
00:00:48,480 --> 00:00:51,280
The disaster relief journey is long and perilous.

2
00:00:51,800 --> 00:00:53,530
I hope Teacher returns safely.

3
00:00:53,720 --> 00:00:54,920
When that time comes,

4
00:00:55,040 --> 00:00:57,370
I will host a welcome banquet for Teacher.

5
00:01:17,720 --> 00:01:18,520
Don't worry.

6
00:01:19,440 --> 00:01:21,100
Chancellor Shen will be fine.

7
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:25,960
Your Majesty.

8
00:01:27,240 --> 00:01:28,039
Your Majesty.

9
00:01:29,240 --> 00:01:31,560
Because Chancellor Shen insisted on leading the relief efforts personally,

10
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:34,620
he was secretly poisoned and is in critical condition.

11
00:01:37,960 --> 00:01:39,920
I know. You may leave.

12
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:56,340
This is the chess set Teacher gave me.

13
00:01:57,600 --> 00:01:59,560
I can't lose it. I can't lose it.

14
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:20,040
The game is set.

15
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:22,560
A move made cannot be taken back.

16
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:23,820
The only thing we can do

17
00:02:24,640 --> 00:02:26,840
is to ensure his efforts are not in vain.

18
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:29,520
If you dare touch Chancellor Shen,

19
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:31,360
I will go after you, Zhou Hong.

20
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:39,320
Experiencer's character goal is 60% complete.

21
00:02:43,200 --> 00:02:44,880
Greetings, Your Majesty.

22
00:02:57,880 --> 00:02:58,680
Your Majesty.

23
00:02:58,800 --> 00:03:00,330
I have something to report.

24
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:04,160
I said there is no court today.

25
00:03:04,920 --> 00:03:07,000
What brings you here?

26
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:11,560
This is a matter of utmost urgency.

27
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:12,680
Oh?

28
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:16,079
I want to report Chancellor Shen Qingyan.

29
00:03:16,079 --> 00:03:17,240
He used the disaster relief as an excuse

30
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,680
to commit corruption.

31
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:21,520
Almost all the funds allocated for the disaster relief

32
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:24,079
were privately embezzled by him.

33
00:03:24,079 --> 00:03:27,079
Rumor has it that he appears to be honest and upright,

34
00:03:27,720 --> 00:03:30,650
but actually has a mountain of gold outside the city.

35
00:03:30,720 --> 00:03:31,520
Your Majesty.

36
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:35,520
I think he shouldn't return to the capital.

37
00:03:36,440 --> 00:03:38,700
He should just be dismissed from office.

38
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:40,780
Yes, Your Majesty.

39
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:42,200
Such a treacherous official

40
00:03:42,200 --> 00:03:43,400
should not stay in Donglin.

41
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:44,240
Your Majesty.

42
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:46,520
This Chancellor Shen is two-faced.

43
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:48,850
He truly deserves to die a thousand times.

44
00:03:49,640 --> 00:03:50,200
Exactly.

45
00:03:54,320 --> 00:03:56,320
The Shen family has all passed away.

46
00:03:57,079 --> 00:03:59,140
What right do you have to slander him?

47
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:01,480
Th-There's evidence.

48
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:05,210
Take a look if you don't believe me.

49
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:16,120
Whether Chancellor Shen has a mountain of gold

50
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:18,180
outside the city or not, I don't know.

51
00:04:18,279 --> 00:04:19,480
But Chancellor Zhou,

52
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:22,580
you have more than just one gold mine.

53
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:26,960
Your Majesty, you cannot say such things.

54
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,480
Look closely.

55
00:04:34,760 --> 00:04:36,490
Every single piece of evidence

56
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:39,010
was collected by Chancellor Shen,

57
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:41,330
who worked tirelessly to get them.

58
00:04:51,760 --> 00:04:52,720
That's not true.

59
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:56,520
Your Majesty, this is not true.

60
00:04:56,520 --> 00:04:58,680
It is that old scoundrel Shen Qingyan.

61
00:04:58,680 --> 00:05:00,810
You don't deserve to mention his name.

62
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:03,320
Men, drag him out and execute him.

63
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:04,440
Your Majesty.

64
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:05,720
Your Majesty.

65
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:06,920
Please spare my life.

66
00:05:06,960 --> 00:05:07,760
Your Majesty.

67
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,120
Save me, Your Majesty.

68
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:10,720
I am innocent, Your Majesty.

69
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:11,520
Wait.

70
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:16,280
Spare my life, Your Majesty.

71
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:34,600
Your Majesty.

72
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:39,480
Your Majesty.

73
00:05:57,200 --> 00:05:59,000
Who else wants to try this sword?

74
00:06:06,840 --> 00:06:10,040
That piece of trash actually killed Zhou Hong,

75
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:13,560
and made his trusted aides the Left and Right Prime Ministers.

76
00:06:14,280 --> 00:06:15,360
It seems

77
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:18,040
he's going to make a move on me.

78
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:20,400
Leave us.

79
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:42,840
Si Xingxuan.

80
00:06:43,320 --> 00:06:43,920
Get out!

81
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:45,880
What happened?

82
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:47,560
Get out!

83
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:49,260
Get out of here!

84
00:06:52,400 --> 00:06:53,480
Put your sword down first.

85
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:54,360
Get out.

86
00:06:58,120 --> 00:06:59,080
What do you mean?

87
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:03,640
Now that Eunuch Sun and Zhou Hong,

88
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:06,040
who were holding you back, are dead,

89
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:08,200
are you going to disregard our partnership

90
00:07:08,200 --> 00:07:09,520
and kick me out?

91
00:07:11,440 --> 00:07:12,440
Or is it

92
00:07:13,880 --> 00:07:15,340
because you've grown soft

93
00:07:17,080 --> 00:07:18,920
on the Grand Princess?

94
00:07:32,280 --> 00:07:33,320
Si Xingxuan.

95
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:39,200
I was wrong about you.
